{
  "stem": "20616.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And said, those tests that you took were about this and this and that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we'd like to send you to University of Alabama where you're going to get another set of tests.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was very happy, because I heard that we were supposed to be shipped out to some sort of an infantry division.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And anything to get out of the infantry was, was something to look forward to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were actually treated like gentlemen rather than like ordinary soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to the-- to Tuscaloosa to the University of Alabama, were given a battery of tests.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one test in particular I had a lot of fun with was a language aptitude test.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were given an imaginary language, an imaginary set of vocabularies, an imaginary set of grammatical rules, and then were given a paragraph to translate into that imaginary language and another paragraph from that imaginary language to translate into English.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought that was, was great.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I was always very, very conscious of language and grammar, having studied Latin a little bit and French and also English.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had no problem with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And apparently, I did fairly well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they sent me to army specialized training program at Haverford College.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, they had a section teaching German and Italian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had my choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Said, do you want to go to the German section or do you want to go to the Italian section?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, well, can I-- shall I go to the German section and am able to goof off, or I'll go to the Italian section.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Might as well learn the language, learn-- get something out of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I opted for the Italian section.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
